							✅ Install via npm
						</p>
						<%- include('./_includes/components/code-block',{
							src: "./code-samples/bash1.ejs",
							lang: "bash",
						}) %>
					</li>
					<li class="Ps-r P1u;5u Lnh1.5 C-$accent850">
						<p>
							✅ And configure by yourself
						</p>
						<%- include('./_includes/components/code-block',{
							src: "./code-samples/scss1.ejs",
							lang: "scss",
						}) %>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

		</article>


		<div class="P8u;0 Fns3.2u W100p Mxw62u">
			<%- include('./_includes/components/link-button.ejs',{
				url: "https://mlutcss.github.io/mlut/",
				text: "Try now",
				icon: "right-triangle"
			}) %>
		</div>

	</div>
</section>



